        <Parent_String>light rail transit [300155876], rail transit systems [300155844], public transit by form [300155843], public transit (infrastructure) [300155835], transit systems (infrastructure) [300008556], infrastructural systems [300155846], systems by function [300242038], systems (equipment) [300008550], Object Groupings and Systems (hierarchy name) [300241489], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
